{"tid":2420824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"失業借貸 ｜呢個係憑我自己本事借來的8萬蚊，點解要還？","createTime":"2021-02-24T06:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T06:31:05.000Z","uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7cfdb8efc0aaed58fb54b629e23fa182a8be5841","tid":2420824,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母🖕🏻<br />\n<br />\n政府拒設立失業援助金，反而建議為失業人士設立「失業借貸」，貸款額上限為失業的申請人在職期間平均每月收入的6倍，上限8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n首12個月只須還息，之後本金連利息最長可攤分5年償還，年利率固定一厘。申請人如按時全額還款，已繳付的利息將全數退還；自由職業人士如證明失去收入亦可申請。<br />\n<br />\n政府總擔保額為150億元，申請期為6個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLqfHI8nmqL/?igshid=ypv1lkk58q3v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLqfHI8nmqL%2F%3Figshid%3Dypv1lkk58q3v&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmxZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=d2b99ee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLqfHI8nmqL%2F%3Figshid%3Dypv1lkk58q3v&h=b75d278a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLqfHI8nmqL/?igshid=ypv1lkk58q3v</a>"},{"pid":"5068efce406f7143ee77055d07dcdef07c5eaae7","tid":2420824,"uid":53601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:21:28.000Z","msg":"蘋果條友係咪有mon po<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b5fabb77a57c26a33e58106235fb1876500387","tid":2420824,"uid":369011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"偉 係到嗎☺️"},{"pid":"a8ddb91113cdf83810ea0609949b6e224240ed03","tid":2420824,"uid":40388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"冇工返仲要借貸<br />\n真。負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}